title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: The Strong Man Badal
subTitle: Madhu falls in love with Ramu, a boy from her college. However, her mother insults him and has intentions of killing him.

title: Mahabali Bal Ganesh VI
subTitle: Top, Dhoti and Suitboot land on Kailash Parbat where they meet Nandi and Mooshak Raj. There, they come across stories about Bal Ganesh, who fights to rid the world of demons.

title: Intelligent
subTitle: DSP Ranjith Kalidoss battles both a serial killer and his own Parkinson's disease. However, his pursuit exposes a more elaborate and sinister scheme than he initially suspected.

title: Main Hi Raja Main Hi Mantri
subTitle: A moneylender is living a happily married life. However, when his wife is insulted by the village sarpanch's wife, he focuses all of his energy on becoming a powerful politician.

title: Vishal in Laatti Charge
subTitle: Muruganantham, a dedicated police constable, is trapped in a high-rise with his son, forced to fight ruthless enemies while protecting the boy and finding a way to escape.

title: Captain
subTitle: A captain leads his team of soldiers inside a forest to investigate mysterious disappearances. However, they soon realise that the danger is more than they bargain for.

title: Darbar
subTitle: Aaditya, a high-ranking law enforcement official, sets out to eradicate the city's gangsters. As the events unfold, it becomes clear that his motivations are deeply personal.

title: Main hoon Surya Singham 2
subTitle: An undercover police officer works in a school and tries to put an end to the criminal activities of two criminals who rule the area.

title: Kabali
subTitle: When Kabali raises his voice against the oppression faced by Tamil labourers in Malaysia, he is imprisoned for 25 years. After being released, he seeks revenge on the ones who wronged him.

title: Kabali
subTitle: When Kabali raises his voice against the oppression faced by Tamil labourers in Malaysia, he is imprisoned for 25 years. After being released, he seeks revenge on the ones who wronged him.

title: Aaj Ka Naya Khiladi
subTitle: Siva unknowingly crosses a ruthless gangster while robbing the Home Minister's residence. Subsequently, the gangster kidnaps the Minister's daughter in retribution.

title: Sivudu
subTitle: A carefree young man's life is disrupted by rising crime in his locality and when his family faces danger, he decides to fight back.

title: Pattathu Arasan
subTitle: Poththaari, a former kabaddi player, lives a happy life with his extended family. However, a tragic death sparks a severing of familial bonds and a fight over Poththaari's land.

title: Anjaniputra
subTitle: A businessman saves a policeman from a group of thugs. As a result, he incurs the wrath of a ruthless local gangster who is also an assassin.

title: Big Brother
subTitle: Sachi dreams of a tranquil life with his family after serving his time in prison. However, fate has other plans for the ex-convict when he encounters a dangerous drug lord.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Zombie Reddy
subTitle: Chaos ensue as Mario, a game developer, and his gang of friends get entangled in a family feud and an enigmatic zombie attack in Rayalaseema, while attending a friend's wedding.

title: Veera Simha Reddy
subTitle: Jai Simha Reddy, the son of the esteemed Veera Simha Reddy, returns home to avenge his father's death as a result of village politics.

title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: Meri Zindagi Ek Agneepath
subTitle: Ramakrishna, a mechanic, is framed for the murder of his wife by his father-in-law who then takes his son away from him. Following his release, Ramakrishna sets out to find his child.

title: Super Ranga
subTitle: Ranga, a reckless thrill-seeker, falls in love with Swathi who makes him promise to be more responsible. However, she breaks up with him when he goes back to his old ways.

title: Garam
subTitle: Varala, a jobless young man, leaves his home to prove himself to his father. However, before achieving his goal, he falls in love with Sameera and tries to woo and save her from gangster Biju.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: An NRI medical student falls in love with a vivacious woman. However, they face challenges in their relationship due to their differences in personalities.

title: Rudhran
subTitle: A man's life takes an unexpected turn when he stumbles upon a criminal network. Determined to bring the truth to light, he sets out to expose the nefarious organisation and protect his loved ones.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Kali Kitaab
subTitle: When narratives from a cryptic book spring to life, a woman experiences bizarre phenomena and resolves to uncover the identity of its enigmatic writer.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Atma Ka Khel
subTitle: A woman named Devi becomes her village's resident exorcist and tries to solve their paranormal problems by using her skills to the maximum.
